arity with digital acquisition channels (PPC, SEO, social, email) and how affiliates use them to drive traffic.\n* High ownership mindset, ability to work independently, and readiness to be fully accountable for the affiliate channel metrics.\n\n*What success looks like*:\n\n* A growing base of active digital affiliates generating high‑quality, compliant traffic and FTDs at or below target CAC.\n* Clear, consistent analytics and reporting for the affiliate channel, with regular optimizations to partner mix, creatives, and deals.\n* Strong reputation and relationships in the affiliate space, with low fraud rates and high partner satisfaction.\n\nPay: From AED18,000.00 per hour\n\n\n\nApplication Question(s):\n* Do you have more than 3 years of experience in Forex or crypto industry? \n* Do you have proven track record of launching or scaling affiliate programs and delivering measurable growth? \n* What is your expected salary? (AED/Monthly)\n* What is your notice period ?\n\nWork Location: Hybrid remote in Jumeirah"}
