{"source":"indeed","source_id":"https://www.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=6a36d8fa2b6102f3","title":"Payment Integration Operation Manager","company":"Binance","location":"{\"city\":\"Abu Dhabi\",\"postalCode\":null,\"country\":\"UAE\",\"countryCode\":\"AE\",\"formattedAddressLong\":\"Abu Dhabi\",\"formattedAddressShort\":\"Abu Dhabi\",\"latitude\":24.46,\"longitude\":54.36,\"streetAddress\":null,\"fullAddress\":null}","remote":false,"salary":"{}","posted_at":"a month ago","url":"https://www.indeed.com/viewjob?jk=6a36d8fa2b6102f3","description":"Binance is a leading global blockchain ecosystem behind the world’s largest cryptocurrency exchange by trading volume and registered users. We are trusted by 300+ million people in 100+ countries for our industry-leading security, user fund transparency, trading engine speed, deep liquidity, and an unmatched portfolio of digital-asset products. Binance offerings range from trading and finance to education, research, payments, institutional services, Web3 features, and more. We leverage the power of digital assets and blockchain to build an inclusive financial ecosystem to advance the freedom of money and improve financial access for people around the world.\nResponsibilities\nWork directly with merchants and PSP partners to guide them through the full integration lifecycle, from solution design and API integration to testing, go-live, and post-launch support.\nLead technical discussions with merchant product and engineering teams to design optimal integration approaches using Binance payment solutions.\nAct as the primary liaison between merchants, product managers, and engineering teams to ensure smooth communication and efficient problem solving.\nProvide hands-on support during merchant integrations, helping troubleshoot technical issues and ensuring a high integration success rate.\nEducate merchants on integration best practices, API usage, and optimal payment flows for both web and mobile environments.\nSupport merchants in de