* Real-time hands-on experience in Education Sales\n* Professional training in admissions counseling\n* Lead generation and sales funnel management exposure\n* Communication and negotiation skill development\n* Internship certificate + performance-based job opportunity\n\nInternship Benefits\n\n* Monthly Stipend / Incentive Based (As per company policy)\n* Sales performance bonus\n* Completion Certificate\n* Potential full-time employment opportunity based on performance\n\nKPIs / Performance Metrics\n\n* Number of leads generated per week\n* Number of calls/follow-ups completed\n* Demo/counseling appointments scheduled\n* Enrollment conversions achieved\n* CRM update accuracy\n\nWork Location: Hybrid remote in Sharjah (Sharjah)"}
